title: TERRIFIC TWO BEDROOM IN BRICKELL! LOOK NO MORE
posting_body: ['Listing ID 4550991', 'This apartment located in a brand new rental community in Miami features wheelchair access, spacious living rooms,', 'private patios/balconies, an elevator, central A/C, laundry in-unit, european-style kitchen, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, nest thermostats, electronic unit entries,', 'ceramic tile floors, and floor to ceiling windows.', 'Community offers a resident lounge with fireplace and television, e-kitchen, pool with sundeck and cabana, fitness center with peloton equipment,', 'outdoor grilling station, outdoor gaming lounge, aqua lounge, work rooms, and bike storage and repair station and air capability.', 'Parking available off-street and electric car charging stations accessible.', 'Pet friendly.', 'Deleaded.', 'Located within 5-10 minutes of Olympia Theatre, Frost Museum of Science, Saks Fifth Avenue, Brickell Center Mall, Bayfront Park and many restaurants nearby.', 'LISTING ID 4550991', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', 'Hannah Edwards', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
